summary: An Ordinance appropriating the sum of $49.43 from the General Fund to pay general taxes existing against lots one (1) to thirteenth (13) inclusive and twenty-three (23) to twenty-five (25) inclusive, block five (5), Edgewater Addition and the first installment of assessment against lot eight (8), block five (5), Edgewater Addition, for the laying off water main in Densmore Avenue, et al, District No. 836, and ordering the drawing of a warrant therefor in favor of the County Treasurer of King County, Washington.
